## ğŸ”Œ API Endpoints

### Roots
```javascript
GET    /api/roots?search=&page=1&limit=10  // Get roots with pagination
POST   /api/roots                          // Add new root
DELETE /api/roots/:root                    // Delete root
POST   /api/roots/upload                   // Upload roots file
```

### Patterns (Schemes)
```javascript
GET    /api/schemes                         // Get all patterns
POST   /api/schemes                         // Add new pattern
PUT    /api/schemes/:name                   // Update pattern
DELETE /api/schemes/:name                   // Delete pattern
POST   /api/schemes/upload                  // Upload patterns file
```

### Generation
```javascript
POST   /api/generate/word                   // Generate single word
       Body: { root, scheme }
       
POST   /api/generate/family                 // Generate word family
       Body: { root }
```

### Validation
```javascript
POST   /api/validate/check                  // Validate word-root pair
       Body: { word, root }
       
POST   /api/validate/decompose              // Decompose word
       Body: { word }
       
POST   /api/validate/find-roots             // Find all possible roots
       Body: { word }
```

### Statistics
```javascript
GET    /api/statistics                      // Get system statistics
```

## ğŸ¨ Styling

The application uses a custom color scheme inspired by traditional Arabic aesthetics:

```css
--primary-dark: #0d3b3f;      /* Deep teal */
--primary-teal: #2d6a6b;      /* Teal */
--accent-gold: #d4a574;       /* Gold */
--accent-cream: #f5e6d3;      /* Cream */
--success-green: #4a7c59;     /* Green */
--danger-red: #a64d4d;        /* Red */
```

### Typography
- **Arabic headers**: Amiri font family
- **Body text**: Cairo font family
- RTL (right-to-left) text direction
- Proper Arabic letter spacing and line height

## ğŸ“± Responsive Design

The application is fully responsive:
- **Desktop**: Full sidebar navigation with two-column layout
- **Tablet**: Collapsible sidebar, adjusted spacing
- **Mobile**: Stacked layout, full-width components

